Megatron's face contorts into a smile, "It took you that long to see 
that? Fools..." He shakes his head.

-------------------------

Switchblade frowns as he looks at the engines, well, the scraps of 
what were engines to be more correct. At a first glance, he could 
see that only about half of what was going to be 
salvagable. "Crap... I get the damn dirty work..." He hops onto the 
pile, and starts to sort through it, pulling out needed pieces and, 
in general, perparing the room as a lab.
